ns0:DescribedValueSet.ns0:Purpose: (Clinical Focus: This grouping of value sets contains concepts that represent placenta previa on the mother's encounter.),(Data Element Scope: This value set may use Quality Data Model (QDM) category related to Diagnosis or Encounter Performed (diagnosis attribute).The intent of this data element is to identify patients with a placenta previa on the mother's encounter.),(Inclusion Criteria: Includes only relevant concepts associated with codes that identify complete or partial placenta previa with or without hemorrhage. This is a grouping of ICD-10-CM and SNOMED CT codes.),(Exclusion Criteria: Excludes concepts that pertain to newborn affected by placenta previa, antepartum hemorrhage due to placenta previa.)
